Table oms.JobDefDO (Enum)

Jobs that are supported from the application by default. These jobs are based on the application job framework.
A job can be attached to a schedule that will execute it.
Note that the job framework is based on a single quartz job of the application server but has no further relations to the other offered quartz jobs.
